{"tid":1222354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾鈺成：暫緩修例可紓怨氣　強推只會港人心中留刺","createTime":"2019-06-14T11:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T13:27:56.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"796bb591edf5501fe16b33d88226dcba519a8392","tid":1222354,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:55:08.000Z","msg":"早前提議將《逃犯條例》修訂草案直接交立法會大會審議的立法會前主席曾鈺成今日（14日）表示，若政府繼續推動修例，難以估計往後的發展，又認為暫緩修例可以紓緩怨氣。<br />\n<br />\n曾鈺成接受now新聞台節目專訪時，引述友人評估稱若立法會通過《逃犯條例》修訂，「暴動㗎喇」，又認為即使不「暴動」、或通過修例後沒有不合理移交個案，政府今次強推修例的「刺」仍會長留港人心中，「他們始終覺得，那麼多人出來反對，政府都繼續去（修例）」。<br />\n<br />\n對於有聲音稱市民反對修例是「有外部勢力介入」，曾鈺成表示，他聽過有「陰謀論角度」稱，背後有人策劃要通過修例衝擊一國兩制，若從這角度思考，暫時放下修例便「不會繼續讓對方有彈藥」衝擊；但如何向支持修例者解釋，「這個當然要做工夫」。"},{"pid":"08850917ab6f1ed9956aed8f449e8d83b7f9f61b","tid":1222354,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:55:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190614/s00001/1560508593498/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190614%2Fs00001%2F1560508593498%2F&d=Q%2BwKghBkVpQFldJLXg3Pjd6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=879b9d9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190614%2Fs00001%2F1560508593498%2F&h=f0c63a69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190614/s00001/1560508593498/</a>"},{"pid":"a85372800c7b0caf740b6ed2792df7dcacdfdf5f","tid":1222354,"uid":2419,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:10:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要撤回</span></span>"},{"pid":"c2dbd56bfa23ddee630c987f9b02219fb2bd16ac","tid":1222354,"uid":176313,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T12:11:17.000Z","msg":"不轍不散，唔好諗住拖"},{"pid":"bbbdbd5e7f095bde2a9e72845e7620509fa68c5a","tid":1222354,"uid":190928,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"